        <num>CC 3495</num>
        <heading>3495.  Commencement and accrual of prescription</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3495.  Commencement and accrual of prescription
This prescription commences to run from the day payment is exigible.  It accrues as to past due payments even if there is a continuation of labor, supplies, or other services.</p>
        </content>
